<div id="wb_element_instance309" class="wb_element" style=" line-height: normal;"><h3 class="wb-stl-heading3" style="text-align: center;"><strong>BUENOS AIRES- EL CALAFATE</strong></h3>

<h3 class="wb-stl-heading3" style="text-align: center;"><strong>7 days, 6 nights</strong></h3>

<p> </p>

<p> </p>

<h2 class="wb-stl-heading2" style="text-align: center;"><strong>The program includes the following services:</strong></h2>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><br><strong>* At Buenos Aires: 3 nights of Lodging in the chosen hotel with breakfast.<br>
* Transfers to Airport / Hotel / Airport /<br>
* Tour along the Buenos Aires City<br>
* At El Calafate: 3 nights of lodging at the chosen hotel with breakfast.<br>
* Transfers Airport/HotelAirport.<br>
* Traditional excursion to the Perito Moreno Glacier.<br>
* Transfers to Airport / Hotel / Airport /<br>
* Dinner Tango`s Show<br>
 </strong></h1>

<h2 class="wb-stl-heading2" style="text-align: center;"><strong style="background-color: transparent;">Day 1: BUENOS AIRES</strong></h2>

<p> </p>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Welcome to the Tango's city, we were waiting for you! Once you arrive the International Airport of Ezeiza, you will be taken to the chosen hotel. During the evening it will fulfil a City Tour to take the first contact with the take care.The rest of the day is free to begin feeling the demurrage At night, lodging.<br>
 </strong></h1>

<h2 class="wb-stl-heading2" style="text-align: center;"><strong style="background-color: transparent;">Day 2: BUENOS AIRES</strong></h2>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"> </h1>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><strong style="background-color: transparent;">Breakfast. It' s time to enjoy Buenos Aires night life. Lodging.</strong></h1>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><strong> </strong></h1>

<h2 class="wb-stl-heading2" style="text-align: center;"><strong style="background-color: transparent;">Day 3: BUENOS AIRES / EL CALAFATE</strong></h2>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><br><strong>Breakfast. Transfer to Airport of Buenos Aires, to flight to the Patagonia. You will step El Calafate, almost feeling the ice from the Glaciers. Transfer from Airport to Chosen hotel. The rest of the day is free. According with your flight time, you could take advantage of the time to do any activity or excursion. The Calafate´s Balcony will give you an introduction just to begin with the adventure. At night and if the weather allows it, you won't forget what a wonderful sky full of starts. Lodging.<br>
 </strong></h1>

<h2 class="wb-stl-heading2" style="text-align: center;"><strong style="background-color: transparent;">Day 4: EL CALAFATE</strong></h2>

<p> </p>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Yes, first of all, your breakfast; because the Perito Moreno's Glacier is not going to escape from us! Very good sheltered and with photo camera prepared for taking a lot of pictures, you'll visit it. Impressive, incredible, isn't it? It wouldn't be easy but you'll have to return. Consult us because in the Estancia Alice you could taste a typical Patagonia barbecue, or even have the continental ices so close to you, with a Walk right upon the Perito Moreno Glacier. Don't worry, you still have another day there. Lodging at the hotel.<br>
 </strong></h1>

<h2 class="wb-stl-heading2" style="text-align: center;"><strong style="background-color: transparent;">Day 5: EL CALAFATE</strong></h2>

<p> </p>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Breakfast. Your day is completely free, but that would be an error. You have a lot of things to do and our suggestions will froze you: in Upsala Explorer you'll be circled by floes, glaciers, patagonic winds and adventure without limit. It will be a day that you'll never forget during the rest of your life. At night, lodging at the hotel.</strong><br>
 </h1>

<h2 class="wb-stl-heading2" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Day 6: EL CALAFATE / BUENOS AIRES</strong></h2>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><br><strong>Breakfast. Transfer to El Calafate´s airport and we assure you: some day you will be return here. Arrive to Buenos Aires airport. In the night Tango Show at Carlos Gardel Corner. Lodging at the chosen hotel.</strong></h1>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"> </h1>

<h2 class="wb-stl-heading2" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Day 7: BUENOS AIRES</strong></h2>

<h1 class="wb-stl-heading1" style="text-align: center;"><br><strong>Breakfast. According with your flight time, you could take advantage of your time to have a walk. Transfer from the hotel to the International Airport Of Ezeiza.</strong></h1>

